          "variable": "59db89d5-4ef2-4b5a-b7ff-818b8efae894",
          "color": "ord-color-seq-4",
          "id": "1cc5ffbb-4217-485b-818e-28359f082f87",
          "text": "To what extent did each person tell you that you could have done more to prevent the incident from occurring?\n"
